copyright work description:
The copyrighted work at issue is many of the images from
www.RosettaStone.com. The main issue at hand is that each of the websites
that are being reported are offering counterfeit Rosetta Stone software
for sale. Rosetta Stone Ltd. is the owner of Rosetta Stone
language-learning software titles. Each of the websites being submitted
are offering counterfeit Rosetta Stone software for sale.

Each of the domains listed below are offering counterfeit Rosetta Stone
software for sale. Please do a site wide removal and block/blacklist each
top level domain listed below from search results.

http://www.rsdis4u.com
